title: Amy’s Daughter Took A Knife To School + The ‘Greatest Inventions’ Draft + Morgan2’s Date Took Her Leftovers…Is That Weird?
itunes:title: Amy’s Daughter Took A Knife To School + The ‘Greatest Inventions’ Draft + Morgan2’s Date Took Her Leftovers…Is That Weird?
description:
Amy’s daughter took a kitchen knife to school and got it taken up after she tried to use it to cut her mango. We do our draft of greatest inventions. Bobby asks Morgan2 about her date with a guy who took her leftovers….she wants to know if it’s weird or not?
